sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 회원/비회원
    participant JSP as list.jsp
    participant C as CommunityPostController
    participant S as CommunityPostServiceImpl
    participant M as CommunityPostMapper
    participant DB as Oracle

    User->>JSP: 탭 클릭 TOWN/SHARE/LIFE
    JSP->>C: GET /community?boardType=TOWN
    C->>S: getTotalPages(boardType, keyword)
    S->>M: selectPostCount
    M->>DB: SELECT COUNT TB_POST
    C->>S: getPostList(boardType, page)
    S->>S: offset = (page-1) x 5
    S->>M: selectPostList
    M->>DB: SELECT TB_POST 페이징
    loop 각 게시글
        S->>M: selectFileUrlsByPostId
        S->>S: attachLifeAnswerPreview
    end
    C-->>JSP: Model list → list.jsp
